# ipv6 address

## example
2a02:a420:0021:3276:f2b1:8492:ab74:c1fa

## size total 128 bits
^= 16 groups of  8 bits;  2 hex digits
^=	8 groups of 16 bits;  4 hex digits
^=	4 groups of 32 bits;  8 hex digits
^=	2 groups of 64 bits; 16 hex digits


## network and node block
network = top (left) 64 bits
node = lower (right) 64 bits
